  "portfolio": [
    {
      "id": "cml7ythx9000mn5n2wobzb49s",
      "title": "GMB Ranker – Local SEO Automation Platform",
      "slug": "gmb-ranker-local-seo-automation-platform",
      "client": "GMB Ranker (In-House Product)",
      "description": "A powerful local SEO platform designed to help businesses and agencies track Google Business Profile rankings, manage reviews, generate AI-powered content, and improve visibility on Google Search and Maps.",
      "image": "/uploads/72ea85f6-ef9b-4188-b8e1-775d6dda999d.jpg",
      "content": "<p data-start=\"614\" data-end=\"988\"><strong data-start=\"614\" data-end=\"634\">Project Overview</strong><br data-start=\"634\" data-end=\"637\">GMB Ranker is a comprehensive local SEO and Google Business Profile optimization platform built to simplify local search marketing for businesses and agencies. The goal of the project was to create an all-in-one system that provides accurate rank tracking, actionable insights, and automation tools to improve local visibility and customer engagement.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"990\" data-end=\"993\">\n<p data-start=\"995\" data-end=\"1326\"><strong data-start=\"995\" data-end=\"1016\">Problem Statement</strong><br data-start=\"1016\" data-end=\"1019\">Local businesses often struggle with tracking Google Maps rankings, managing reviews, and maintaining an active Google Business Profile. Existing tools were either too complex, expensive, or lacked accurate geo-based data. There was a need for a streamlined platform focused purely on local SEO performance.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"1328\" data-end=\"1331\">\n<p data-start=\"1333\" data-end=\"1638\"><strong data-start=\"1333\" data-end=\"1345\">Solution</strong><br data-start=\"1345\" data-end=\"1348\">GMB Ranker was developed as a centralized dashboard offering grid-based rank tracking, Google Business Profile audits, AI-generated content, review management, and competitor insights. The platform enables users to monitor performance across locations while automating repetitive SEO tasks.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"1640\" data-end=\"1643\">\n<p data-start=\"1645\" data-end=\"1661\"><strong data-start=\"1645\" data-end=\"1661\">Key Features</strong></p>\n<ul data-start=\"1662\" data-end=\"1926\">\n<li data-start=\"1662\" data-end=\"1700\">\n<p data-start=\"1664\" data-end=\"1700\">Geo-grid based local rank tracking</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1701\" data-end=\"1761\">\n<p data-start=\"1703\" data-end=\"1761\">Google Business Profile audits and optimization insights</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1762\" data-end=\"1804\">\n<p data-start=\"1764\" data-end=\"1804\">AI-powered post and content generation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1805\" data-end=\"1850\">\n<p data-start=\"1807\" data-end=\"1850\">Review monitoring and response management</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1851\" data-end=\"1881\">\n<p data-start=\"1853\" data-end=\"1881\">Competitor rank comparison</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1882\" data-end=\"1926\">\n<p data-start=\"1884\" data-end=\"1926\">Free local SEO tools for lead generation</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-start=\"1928\" data-end=\"1931\">\n<p data-start=\"1933\" data-end=\"2283\"><strong data-start=\"1933\" data-end=\"1965\">Development &amp; Implementation</strong><br data-start=\"1965\" data-end=\"1968\">The platform was built with a scalable architecture, focusing on performance, usability, and data accuracy. A clean admin dashboard allows users to manage multiple locations, keywords, and clients efficiently. Special attention was given to UI clarity so even non-technical users can easily understand ranking data.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2285\" data-end=\"2288\">\n<p data-start=\"2290\" data-end=\"2572\"><strong data-start=\"2290\" data-end=\"2310\">Results &amp; Impact</strong><br data-start=\"2310\" data-end=\"2313\">GMB Ranker helps businesses gain better visibility on Google Search and Maps, save time through automation, and make informed SEO decisions using clear ranking data. Agencies can efficiently manage multiple clients while offering measurable local SEO results.</p>\n<hr data-start=\"2574\" data-end=\"2577\">\n<p data-start=\"2579\" data-end=\"2826\"><strong data-start=\"2579\" data-end=\"2593\">Conclusion</strong><br data-start=\"2593\" data-end=\"2596\">GMB Ranker demonstrates a strong blend of product thinking, system design, and SEO automation. It stands as a scalable solution for local businesses and agencies aiming to dominate local search results with data-driven strategies.</p>",
      "seoMetadataId": "cml7ythxa000nn5n22cczvzfi",
      "createdAt": "2026-02-04T11:49:45.597Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-02-04T12:06:15.903Z"
    }
